---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="FORGOR - Privacy Policy">
  <Header />

  <main class="flex-grow flex justify-center px-6 py-16 text-white bg-purple-DEFAULT">
    <section class="max-w-6xl w-full">
      <!-- Page title -->
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-display mb-12 text-center">
        Your Privacy Matters
      </h1>

      <!-- Blocks -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-purple-800 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-neonGreen-DEFAULT mb-3">What We Collect</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90 space-y-2">
            <li>Account info: email, username, hashed password.</li>
            <li>Uploads: files, metadata, and AI-generated tags.</li>
            <li>Usage data: anonymous stats to improve performance.</li>
            <li>Interaction data: clicks and views to refine recommendations.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-purple-800 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-neonGreen-DEFAULT mb-3">How We Use It</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90 space-y-2">
            <li>Run core features like search and summaries.</li>
            <li>Make results and digests more relevant.</li>
            <li>Send you account updates and optional emails.</li>
            <li>Keep accounts secure and block fraud.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-purple-800 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-neonGreen-DEFAULT mb-3">Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90">
            We don’t sell your data. We only use trusted third-party tools (hosting, email, AI services) to keep FORGOR running.  
            We may share info if required by law.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-purple-800 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-neonGreen-DEFAULT mb-3">Security</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90">
            Data is encrypted, passwords are hashed, and access is restricted.  
            We review our security practices regularly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-purple-800 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-neonGreen-DEFAULT mb-3">Your Choices</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90 space-y-2">
            <li>Export your data anytime.</li>
            <li>Update account info in settings.</li>
            <li>Delete your account to remove all data.</li>
            <li>Unsubscribe from emails in the footer.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-purple-800 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-neonGreen-DEFAULT mb-3">Updates</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90">
            If we change this policy, we’ll post it here and notify you if it’s major.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-purple-800 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-none md:col-span-2">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-neonGreen-DEFAULT mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90">
            Questions? Email <a href="mailto:nikhil@forgor.space" class="text-neonGreen-DEFAULT hover:underline">nikhil@forgor.space</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
